# 6x10 leafy office plant — fuller silhouette than the old 4-wide stick
# so it reads as "plant" from across the room. `l` light leaf, `L` dark
# leaf for depth, `n` dark pot rim, `d` darker dirt centre.
@frame 0
. l L l . .
l L l L l .
L l l L L l
l L L l l L
. l l L l .
. . L l . .
. . L L . .
n n n n n n
n d d d d n
n n n n n n
